’Щ@75c19c87a965d5d3510d836e09e4ef108e5fc7ba9e33f483d61f9eb8b4075df9ЪTitle: title: str pascal-case
Path: Examples
Content:
convert a string to PascalCase
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'nu-shell' | str pascal-case
NuShell

```
convert a string to PascalCase
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'this-is-the-first-case' | str pascal-case
ThisIsTheFirstCase

```
convert a string to PascalCase
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'this_is_the_second_case' | str pascal-case
ThisIsTheSecondCase

```
convert a column from a table to PascalCase
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[lang, gems]; [nu_test, 100]] | str pascal-case lang
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ  lang  в”Ӯ gems в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ NuTest в”Ӯ  100 в”Ӯ
